OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of wind and rain across
OL,6,Fnorthwest Scotland will gradually move
OL,7,Fsoutheastwards today, perhaps reaching
OL,8,Fnorthern England and north Wales by
OL,9,Fevening. Ahead of this, any early fog
OL,10,Fclearing but a cloudier day overall
OL,11,Fthan Tuesday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe band of rain will
OL,14,Fcontinue moving southeastwards, but
OL,15,Fgradually petering out. Dry with clear
OL,16,Fspells either side of this with a
OL,17,Fwidespread frost developing across the
OL,18,Fnorth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
