OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy with patchy drizzle
OL,6,Fat first in the far southeast.
OL,7,FOtherwise dry with some sunny spells,
OL,8,Falthough rain arriving into the
OL,9,Fnorthwest later. Temperatures near
OL,10,Faverage for early April.
